## Build Instructions

## Flashing Instructions

Pre-requirment: dfu-programmer

- Reboot the board into DFU bootloader mode by reseting the board while JP1 is short circuited.

- Check if the device is in DFU mode

```
lsusb | grep -i atmel
```

- Erase the flash

```
sudo dfu-programmer atmega32u4 erase
```

- Flash the hex file

```
sudo dfu-programmer atmega32u4 flash leds_firmware.hex
```

(Alternate way)

```
rosrun autonomy_leds flash.sh
```

## Running the driver


Pre-requirement: rosserial-server

```
rosrun rosserial_python serial_node.py _port:=/dev/ttyACM0 _baud:=115200
```


